  |   * Maximum lives in Veteran mode have been changed from 9 to 99        |
  |                                                                         |
  |   * Issues causing the game to lock up have been fixed, and overall     |
  |     game responsiveness has been improved                               |
  |                                                                         |
  |   * Fixed errors in the game script                                     |
  |                                                                         |
  |   * Other various bug fixes                                             |
